freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I have muscle and joint pain. I even have muscle weakness. My pcp wants me to hold off on vaccine. All symptoms started 2 days after and got progressively worse.
Ive had on going joint pain on and off.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Ive been on 40mg of prednisone for 3 day.my tongue is still swollen.
Started steroid tapper and tongue swelled up again..my steroids increased and had to follow up with dr
Still have swollen tongue on 40mg of prednisone.  Seen my ENT and doctor. Now we are going to do a steroid tapper.
Still have tounge swelling.  Doctors were unable to decrease prednisone bc tounge swelling increased.
Throat closed up yesterday. Unable to swallow and eat.  Was in the ED. Now im take prednisone 40mg every day for 4 days. They also gave me an epi pen.
Tongue started swelling worse. Hard to swallow.Im in the ED now.
Tongue swelling having to take benadryl 25mg every 4hrs
Went to the ED my tongue swelled up. Taking benadryl every 4hrs. I got my vaccine yesterday at 4:30pm
